column2: SELECT id AS up_id,  ra AS up_ra,  dec AS up_dec FROM MYDB.input_sample_YN  CREATE TABLE #tmp (   up_id varchar(#),   objid bigint ) INSERT INTO #tmp EXEC spGetNeighbors #    INSERT INTO MYDB.output_sample_YN SELECT a.id, a.ra, a.dec, t.objid as matched_id, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, e.EW_Hb_#, e.EW_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_Hb_#, e.Flux_Hb_#_Err,  e.Sigma_Hb_#, e.Sigma_Hb_#_Err, e.EW_OIII_#, e.EW_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err,e.Sigma_OIII_#,e.Sigma_OIII_#_Err, e.EW_Ha_#,  e.EW_Ha_#_Err,  e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.Sigma_Ha_#, e.Sigma_Ha_#_Err, e.EW_NII_#, e.EW_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_Err,  e.Sigma_NII_#, e.Sigma_NII_#_Err, e.EW_OI_#, e.EW_OI_#_Err, e.Flux_OI_#, e.Flux_OI_#_Err, e.Sigma_OI_#, e.Sigma_OI_#_Err, e.sigmaStars, e.sigmaStarsErr FROM #tmp t   JOIN MYDB.input_sample_YN a ON t.up_id = a.id   JOIN specobj s ON s.bestobjid=t.objid   JOIN emissionLinesPort e on e.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE s.class = &&&
